a say, that's awesome, man.\nI don't know if you've been in a fight before...\nbut there's usually not this much talking.\nAll right, sorry. My bad.\nGuys, look, I'd love to keep this up,\nbut I've only got one job here today...\nand I gotta impress Mr Stark, so, I'm really sorry.\n(YELPS)\n(SCREAMING)\nYou couldn't have done that earlier?\nI hate you.\nGreat.\nHey, Cap, heads-up!\nThrow it at this.\nNow!\nOh, come on!\nOh, man, I thought it was a water truck.\nUh, sorry.", "type": "Document"}}